NK039(ti)019:1: // dpal ldan lha mo srog gi gzer chung gi cho ga'i las 'grigs kyi rim pa bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)019:2: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)019:3: dbang thob cing dam tshig dang ldan pa'i gang zag gis /
NK039(ti)019:4: sngon du phyag na rdo rje'i bsnyen pa dang bsgrub pa'i mtshan ma mthar phyin pa'i gang zag gis /
NK039(ti)019:5: dpal ldan lha mo srog gi gzer chung bsgrub par 'dod pas /
NK039(ti)019:6: 'di la don rnam pa gsum ste /
NK039(ti)019:9: bsnyen pa'i rim pa dang gsum mo //
NK039(ti)019:10: dang po rdzas bsags pa la'ang /
NK039(ti)019:11: bsgrub pa'i rdzas dang brten pa'i rdzas gnyis /
NK039(ti)019:12: dang po bsgrub pa'i rdzas la /
NK039(ti)019:13: dang po gnas dben par bkra shis pa'i sa la man+dala gru bzhi pa gcig byas la /
NK039(ti)019:14: dbus su gru gsum gru gang pa cig bya /
NK039(ti)019:15: de la mi khrag dang khyi khrag rta khrag gsum dang /
NK039(ti)019:16: dur khrod sol ba nag po byas la /
NK039(ti)019:17: de'i kha la rtsang bco brgyad mchog phur gsum dang nyi shu rtsa gcig sbrel bar bkod /
NK039(ti)019:18: dgra gcig yod kyang ling+ga lnga byas la /
NK039(ti)019:19: gsum gru gsum gyi zur gsum du bzhag /
NK039(ti)019:20: gcig g.yag ru rkug pa'i nang du bzhug /
NK039(ti)019:21: gru gsum gyi dbus su bzhag /
NK039(ti)019:22: gcig gi snying gar tshon skud kyi thag pa btags
NK039(ti)019:23: la brten gtor gyi zhabs su bcug gnyis thun rdzas
NK039(ti)019:24: ni mi bsad pa'i mtshon cha dang yungs kar /
NK039(ti)019:34: dug sna mang po las khrag /
NK039(ti)019:35: de nas gru gsum mtho gang ba gcig gi nang du /
NK039(ti)019:36: dam sri 'dre mo'i gzugs la 'gug gzhugs byas la /
NK039(ti)019:37: thun mtshams su rang nyid yi dam gyi sngags sham bu la /
NK039(ti)019:38: dngos grub la bar du gcod pa'i dam sri lte
NK039(ti)019:39: phur nag mo ma ra ya phata ces sogs pa'i
NK039(ti)019:40: rta nag gi rnyig pa dza bzhi bris pa'am /
NK039(ti)019:41: yang na lcags phur gyi btog /
NK039(ti)019:42: gnyis pa brten pa'i rdzas mda' bya rgod ma la dar sna tshogs dang snying sna tshogs dang /
NK039(ti)019:43: stag ras dang ne'u le'i rkyal pa dang /
NK039(ti)019:44: nal ma'i sha khrag dang 'bru sna tshogs phye ma byas la btag go //
NK039(ti)019:45: bud med gzhon nu mtshan ldan chur shi ba'i srin lag la /
NK039(ti)019:46: g.yab dar nag po btags la mdun du btsugs /
NK039(ti)019:47: de nas sha chen tri snying bong bu'i snying mi
NK039(ti)019:48: dbang sha khrag gi gzhi byas pas gtor ma che
NK039(ti)019:50: lha mo'i tsaka li yang btag go //
NK039(ti)019:51: kha dar nag gi bkag la /
NK039(ti)019:52: gzugs byang gi zur la bzhag go //
NK039(ti)019:53: brten rdzas bskang rdzas dam rdzas tshad kyi mtha' bskor /
NK039(ti)019:55: yi dam gyi gtor ma spyi la gzhung ltar bya'o //
NK039(ti)019:56: de rnams ni rdzas bsags pa dang /
NK039(ti)019:58: de nas lam la 'jug pa'i nub mo ling+ga rnams bsdus la sgo rgyab tu khyer la /
NK039(ti)019:59: rang nyid yi dam lha yi nga rgyal gyi ling+ga la 'gugs gzhugs byas la /
NK039(ti)019:60: gu gul dang khyi lud kyi bdug cing lha dbye ba dang bsad las rnams byas la /
NK039(ti)019:61: nang du 'ong la ling+ka thams cad gnas su bkod /
NK039(ti)019:62: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la lha bsgom pa dang bsnyen pa'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)019:63: dang po lha bsgom pa ni /
NK039(ti)019:64: de nas gzhi bdag la gtor ma gtang la /
NK039(ti)019:65: bka' bsgo byas la mthu dpung bcol /
NK039(ti)019:66: bgegs la lan chags gtor ma sbyin la lan chags byang bar bsam /
NK039(ti)019:67: de nas yi dam gzhung ltar byas la /
NK039(ti)019:69: bstod pa bskul ba rnams bya'o //
NK039(ti)019:70: de nas phyag na rdo rje bsgom la bsnyen pa ci mang bya /
NK039(ti)019:71: gzungs ring khyung sngags rnams bzlas la gtor ma bsngo'o //
NK039(ti)019:72: de nas lha mo bsgom snyoms su bskyed /
NK039(ti)019:73: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che dar
NK039(ti)019:74: zhing rgyas pa'i ched du tshad med bzhi bsgom la
NK039(ti)019:75: / swa b+ha was stong par sbyangs /
NK039(ti)019:76: stong pa'i ngang las mdun du yi ge b+h+r+aumhsmuga nag yongs su gyur pa las /
NK039(ti)019:77: thod pa skom rlon las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi pa sgo bzhi pa /
NK039(ti)019:78: zhing chen gyi ka gdung zhing chung gi dral drabs /
NK039(ti)019:83: nyi zla'i skar khung byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:84: de'i steng na zhing gi rgyal mtshan btsugs pa /
NK039(ti)019:85: tog la zhing gi gdug 'khor ba /
NK039(ti)019:86: yangs shing rgya che ba'i gur khang /
NK039(ti)019:87: de'i phyi rol du bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshub ma'i dgu klong rlung gi gur khang /
NK039(ti)019:88: de'i nang du me ri dmar nag 'tshub ma'i gur khang /
NK039(ti)019:89: de'i dbus su mi ro rta ro bsnol zhing 'phyo ba /
NK039(ti)019:90: mi khrag dang rta khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khyil pa /
NK039(ti)019:91: de'i nang du g+har da pa h'u de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK039(ti)019:92: srid pa'i bong bu dmar ka rlung gis gshog pa can /
NK039(ti)019:93: thod skam 'bar ba'i sga bstad pa /
NK039(ti)019:94: srin po'i ya 'gal las snga ru byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:95: srin mo'i 'gal las phyi ru byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:96: mig mjug ma na yod pa /
NK039(ti)019:97: rna ba gnam la slebs pa /
NK039(ti)019:99: srin po'i lpags pa las sga g.yog byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:100: gong thag dang glo snyed sbrul la byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:101: rus sbal nag po'i pho ku btab pa /
NK039(ti)019:102: snga shad g.yas nas bdud kyi khram bam /
NK039(ti)019:103: g.yon nas tshon gyi gru gu /
NK039(ti)019:104: phyi shad g.yas na byang dmar bam po /
NK039(ti)019:105: g.yon nas nad kyi rkyal pa /
NK039(ti)019:106: mi mgo'i thod dam byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:107: snyed smed la mi lag 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)019:108: ba su ta'i zhags pa'i mthur chings su byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:109: nam mkha' las mched pa lta bu gcig bskyed /
NK039(ti)019:110: de'i sga gong du zhing chen bsnol ba'i steng du
NK039(ti)019:111: bam las pad+ma ram las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK039(ti)019:112: steng du b+h+yohnaga mo gcig bsam /
NK039(ti)019:113: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las b+h+yo phar 'phros gdan thog gi b+h+yo la thim par bsam /
NK039(ti)019:115: dgra bgegs gdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad tshur 'dus b+h+yo la thim /
NK039(ti)019:116: ral gri b+h+yo yi mtshan pa gcig tu gyur /
NK039(ti)019:117: b+h+yo de yongs su gyur pa las dpal ldan lha mo sku mdog mthing nag rngam pa /
NK039(ti)019:118: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa spyan gsum dmar la zlum pa /
NK039(ti)019:119: ral pa kham nag las me stag dmar tsig tsig 'phro ba /
NK039(ti)019:120: phyag g.yas ral gri sdig pa can nam mkhar phyar ba /
NK039(ti)019:121: g.yon pas thod pa lcang lo can khrag gis bkang ba thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK039(ti)019:122: mchan na ne'u le'i rkyal pa'i kha nas rin po che 'phur ba'i tshul du 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)019:123: ral pa dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa'i skra mtshams
NK039(ti)019:124: nas thod pa skam po lnga yi dbu la brgyan
NK039(ti)019:125: pa'i steng du / rin po che'i rtse bran lnga'i brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)019:126: spyi bo nas zla ba shar ba /
NK039(ti)019:127: lte ba nas nyi ma shar ba /
NK039(ti)019:128: spyi gtsug na rma bya'i rgyal mtshan btsugs pa /
NK039(ti)019:129: rna ba g.yas pa'i gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'i thog tu seng ge 'gying ba /
NK039(ti)019:130: g.yon na sbrul nag gi gdeng ga 'phyo ba /
NK039(ti)019:131: snyan cha gnyis na gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK039(ti)019:132: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK039(ti)019:133: glang po che'i ko ba rlon pa'i stod g.yogs shing /
NK039(ti)019:134: stag lpags kyis sham thabs dang mi rtsis kyi re ldes sku smad dkris pa /
NK039(ti)019:135: thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal byas pa /
NK039(ti)019:136: rus pa dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis sku dang yan lag thams cad brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)019:137: de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du b+h+yo nag mo gcig 'khor ba /
NK039(ti)019:138: de'i mthar sngags kyi g.yon bskor du 'khor ba'o //
NK039(ti)019:139: b+h+yo de las nag mo 'bum spros pa'i 'khor bdud
NK039(ti)019:140: mo 'bum sde sku mdog nag mo ral pa thur
NK039(ti)019:141: du phyal ba / g.yas gri gug dang g.yon thod khrag thogs pa /
NK039(ti)019:142: mchan na nad kyi rkyal ba sngo dmar 'chang ba /
NK039(ti)019:143: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi sku la mnab pa /
NK039(ti)019:144: 'jigs 'jigs rngam rngam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ba'i
NK039(ti)019:145: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi spyi bor 'khor lo dkar
NK039(ti)019:146: po rtsibs bzhi pa'i steng du dkar po /
NK039(ti)019:147: mgrin par pad+ma dmar po 'dabs ma bzhi pa'i lte bar +aahdamara po /
NK039(ti)019:148: thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje sngon po
NK039(ti)019:149: rtsa lnga pa'i lte bar h'u sngon pos mtshan par
NK039(ti)019:150: gyur / sh+r+ai d+ae wi ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti badz+ra d+aa ki ne phem /
NK039(ti)019:151: bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'i h'u 'od zer 'phros pas
NK039(ti)019:152: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas bsgom pa dang 'dra ba'i
NK039(ti)019:154: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:155: srin lag g.yab dar thogs la tshil chen dang spos dud kyi gsur btang /
NK039(ti)019:157: b+han+d+ha stag sprod kyi rnga brdungs la /
NK039(ti)019:158: 'bar ba'i phyag rgyas dpral ba'i dbyings su bskor la /
NK039(ti)019:159: ngag tu phem zhes brjod la /
NK039(ti)019:160: bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pa'i mdun gyi lha mo'i thugs kar phog /
NK039(ti)019:161: de'i thugs kar nas 'od zer 'phros pas byang shar
NK039(ti)019:162: gyi mtshams phyogs bcur 'phros pa'i lha mo ye shes
NK039(ti)019:163: pa'i thugs kar phog pas sngon gyi thugs dam rjes
NK039(ti)019:164: su dran nas / lha mo 'khor bcas bdud mo
NK039(ti)019:165: 'bum gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa mdun du byon
NK039(ti)019:166: su dran nas / par bsam la / spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK039(ti)019:168: rlung nag dgu rlung 'tshubs ma 'khyil ba'i dbus //
NK039(ti)019:169: rin chen pho brang thod pa'i sku mkhar dbus //
NK039(ti)019:170: nyi zla'i gdan bshams mdzes pa'i rol mos brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:171: dung sgo dkar mor shel gyi skas btsugs te //
NK039(ti)019:172: rdzu 'phrul grub pa'i gnas 'dir spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)019:173: dbang phyug gtso mo lha mo nag mo'i sku //
NK039(ti)019:174: bstan pa bsrung ba'i bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:175: mthing nag gcer bu khrag gi ral pa can //
NK039(ti)019:176: nag mo za byed rngam pa'i mche ba can //
NK039(ti)019:177: dbu skra mthon mthing lcang lor nam mkhar 'khyil //
NK039(ti)019:178: gser dang mu tig g.yu yi lan phran can //
NK039(ti)019:179: dbu rgyan mgul chur thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:180: chags pa'i spyan rtsa dmar po glog ltar 'gyu //
NK039(ti)019:181: sgegs pa'i cha lugs rna ba seng ges brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:182: do shal phyag gdub dpung rgyan sbrul gyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:183: drag po'i stobs ldan khrag gi mchil ris can //
NK039(ti)019:184: 'jig rten gsal ba'i nyi zla'i sgron mes brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:185: dur khrod dbang mdzad zhing lpags re lde gsol //
NK039(ti)019:186: phyag mtshan ral gris dug gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK039(ti)019:187: b+han+d+ha dmar pos bdud kyi dmag dpung sgrol //
NK039(ti)019:188: khram bam nag pos skye 'gro rtsis la 'debs //
NK039(ti)019:189: nad kyi rkyal pas bstan pa gnyen po bsrung //
NK039(ti)019:190: mi 'bral gzugs mdzes lcags sgrog mdzes pas brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:191: myur mgyogs mthu ldan bdud mo dril zhon ma //
NK039(ti)019:192: bdag gis bsgrub pa'i gnas 'dir spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)019:193: sprul pa'i phyag brnyan klu mo chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)019:194: bka' yi blon mo ba lam dril sna ma //
NK039(ti)019:195: las kyi pha nya khri sman sa le ma //
NK039(ti)019:196: slad kyi rjes 'brang seng ge'i gdong pa can //
NK039(ti)019:197: 'khor bcas spyan 'dren gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:198: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti /
NK039(ti)019:199: e h+ya hi a kar sha ya dza dzah dza h'u bam ho /
NK039(ti)019:202: ma yi nang na ma gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:203: sring gi nang na sring gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:204: dpal ldan gnyen gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:205: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)019:206: 'dod pa'i khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)019:207: lha'i gnas na lha mo nam gru ma //
NK039(ti)019:208: klu'i gnas na klu mo glog 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)019:209: srin gyi gnas nas srin mo sham sham ma //
NK039(ti)019:210: mi'i gnas nas bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:211: mi'i bdud las khyod pas che ba med //
NK039(ti)019:212: gnas ni byang shar mtshams na gnas //
NK039(ti)019:213: rgyu ni bar snang khams na rgyu //
NK039(ti)019:215: rkang gdub lcags kyi lhwam gyon ma //
NK039(ti)019:216: sku la mdzes pa'i re lde gsol //
NK039(ti)019:217: mi mgo rta mgo mkhar du brtsigs //
NK039(ti)019:218: thod pa dgu brtsegs gzhal yas nas //
NK039(ti)019:219: ma cig lha mo spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)019:220: do nub nam gyi dgung thun la //
NK039(ti)019:221: ming po rdo rjes las bcol nas //
NK039(ti)019:222: sring mo dam can las mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)019:223: brnag pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:224: ma bos pa'i tshe na snyan ma sra //
NK039(ti)019:225: g.yab pa'i tshe na spyan ma rtul //
NK039(ti)019:226: bsgrub pa'i tshe na rgyang ma ring //
NK039(ti)019:227: mngag pa'i tshe na bang ma bul //
NK039(ti)019:228: rbad pa'i tshe na mthu ma chung //
NK039(ti)019:229: dam rdzas brgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)019:230: bdag gis bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:232: srin lag g.yab dar gang rung la /
NK039(ti)019:233: b+h+r+aum h'u b+h+yo dzah mi dbang tri khrag gis bris la mdun du lha mo dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK039(ti)019:234: rang nyid yi dam gyi mdun gyi g.yab dar yi
NK039(ti)019:235: ge dang bcas pa'i 'od zer dza yi rnam pa
NK039(ti)019:236: can 'phros pas / byang shar mtshams nas lha mo
NK039(ti)019:237: bzhugs pas thugs ka'i b+h+yo la dza'i 'khyud pa'i dus
NK039(ti)019:238: sngon gyi thugs dam dran nas rang dbang med par
NK039(ti)019:239: g.yab dar g.yab pa tsam gyis byon par bsams la
NK039(ti)019:240: can 'phros pas / / mdun gyi dam tshig pa dang gnyis su med par bsams la /
NK039(ti)019:242: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK039(ti)019:243: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs dpal ldan ma //
NK039(ti)019:244: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:245: bdag gis gdungs te bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)019:246: nyi ma byang shar pha gi nas //
NK039(ti)019:247: yongs 'dus shing gi rtsa ba nas //
NK039(ti)019:248: mtsho mu le mthing gi nang shed nas //
NK039(ti)019:249: mthing shog sngon po'i gur nang nas //
NK039(ti)019:250: thod pa le brtsigs gzhal yas nas //
NK039(ti)019:251: bse yi sku mkhar grub bzhi'i nang //
NK039(ti)019:252: rin chen sna bdun pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)019:253: mi ro rta ro gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)019:254: mi khrag rta khrag 'dam rdzabs stangs //
NK039(ti)019:255: de na ma gcig lha mo bzhugs //
NK039(ti)019:256: lha mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:257: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:258: 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)019:259: chibs su bong bu dmar gwa bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:260: khal du lcags kyi dra ba mig dgu 'gel //
NK039(ti)019:261: mchan nas nad kyi rkyal pa thong //
NK039(ti)019:262: g.yas na ral gri sdig pa can //
NK039(ti)019:263: g.yon na gdug pa'i thod khrag thogs //
NK039(ti)019:264: stong gsum kun gyi b+h+yo lugs mkhan //
NK039(ti)019:265: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:266: dam tshig dbang gis spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)019:267: dam la ma 'da' da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)019:268: ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:269: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum dang bcas //
NK039(ti)019:270: rnal 'byor bdag gis gdung te bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)019:271: mchil ma thul thul ma thogs myur du byon //
NK039(ti)019:272: ma cig lha mo nag mo khyed //
NK039(ti)019:273: sngon tshe phyag na rdo rje la //
NK039(ti)019:274: rang rtags srog gi snying po phul //
NK039(ti)019:275: bos na 'ong bar khas blangs shing //
NK039(ti)019:276: khas blangs dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)019:277: rnal 'byor bdag gis khyod bskul na //
NK039(ti)019:278: dam tshig dbang gis da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)019:279: thugs dam dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:280: ma cig lha mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)019:281: na chung mtshan ldan chur shi ba'i //
NK039(ti)019:282: srin lag g.yab mos spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)019:283: mi dbang smin pa'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)019:284: dam rdzas 'di la myur du byon //
NK039(ti)019:285: e a ra li re ma ti sa ma ya
NK039(ti)019:286: dza dzah dza h'u bam hoh dam tshig pa dang
NK039(ti)019:289: b+h+yoh ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:290: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum phrag rnams //
NK039(ti)019:291: mi ro gshibs pa'i gdan mchog dang //
NK039(ti)019:292: srin po'i bong bu'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK039(ti)019:293: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK039(ti)019:296: ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:297: nag mo chen mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)019:298: pho nya bdud mo 'bum tshogs la //
NK039(ti)019:299: bdag cag dad pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)019:300: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti a ti pu ho pra ti dza ho /
NK039(ti)019:301: de nas dam bsre ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:303: rdo rje dri chu bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK039(ti)019:304: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar //
NK039(ti)019:305: dam tshig snying khrag chen mo 'di //
NK039(ti)019:306: bsres pa'i mchog ste srog gis snying //
NK039(ti)019:307: ma gcig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)019:308: khyod dang bdag nyid dam basre'o //
NK039(ti)019:309: rtag tu dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)019:310: dam la 'da' bas bsreg par byed //
NK039(ti)019:311: ma h+aa ku ku sa ma ya ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK039(ti)019:312: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)019:313: dbang gi lha rnams spyan drangs /
NK039(ti)019:314: khyed rnams kyi 'di la mngon par dbang bskur du gsol /
NK039(ti)019:315: zhes gsol ba btab pa'i de rnams kyi ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i bkang ba'i bum pa thogs nas /
NK039(ti)019:316: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka te sa ma ya sh+ri ye h'u /
NK039(ti)019:317: zhes dbang bskur lus gang dri ma dag chu yi
NK039(ti)019:318: lhag ma spyi gtsug tu gnas pa yongs su gyur
NK039(ti)019:319: pa las / rdo rje 'jigs byed yum dang bcas pas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK039(ti)019:320: phyag na rdo rje yin par bsam /
NK039(ti)019:321: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:323: bdud mo bye ba 'bum gyi gtso mo ni //
NK039(ti)019:324: dpal ldan gnyen gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:325: khyod la dpyid gsum mchod pa dam pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:326: spos sbyor sa yi bdud rtsi rnam lnga dang //
NK039(ti)019:327: tri rgod snying dang rak+ta ga bur dang //
NK039(ti)019:328: 'tshubs nag rlung gi bsdus pa'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK039(ti)019:329: ma dpyid kyi rgyal mo'i thugs dam bskang bar mdzod /
NK039(ti)019:331: dpal ldan gnyen gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:332: ma khyod la dbyar gsum mchod pa dam pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:333: spos sbyor pa yi bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK039(ti)019:334: me tog chu skyes thang skyes rnam par sbyar //

NK039(ti)019:339: dpal ldan gnyen gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:340: ma khyod la ston gsum mchod pa dam pa 'bul ba ni //

NK039(ti)019:342: shing tog sna tshogs sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi dang //
NK039(ti)019:343: go ro tsa na'i bardzesa pa'i rdzas mchog 'dis //
NK039(ti)019:344: ma ston gyi rgyal mo'i thugs dam bskang bar mdzod /
NK039(ti)019:346: dpal ldan gnyen gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:347: ma khyod la dgun gsum mchod pa dam pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:348: bsad pa'i sha dang myos pa'i chang //
NK039(ti)019:349: bsregs pa'i gsur dang rlon pa'i sha //

NK039(ti)019:351: 'bras bu mi dbang smin pa'i sha /
NK039(ti)019:352: tshil chen dri dang bdug spos rnams //
NK039(ti)019:353: ma dgun gyi rgyal mo'i thugs dam bskang bar mdzod /
NK039(ti)019:355: ma cig bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:356: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum sde la //
NK039(ti)019:358: rgya mtsho 'bab chu chu mig rdzings //
NK039(ti)019:360: ma yi sku la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:361: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti sa pa ri wa ra ar+g+ham pra tits+tshi h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)019:362: chu skyes thang skyes me tog dang //
NK039(ti)019:363: dbang po lnga yi me tog 'di //
NK039(ti)019:364: ma yi dbu la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:365: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:366: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:368: push+pe ga bur gla rtsi gu gul dang //
NK039(ti)019:369: sha chen spos kyi dud pa 'di //
NK039(ti)019:370: ma yi shang la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:371: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:372: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:373: d+hup+pe nyi zla glog dang gsal ba'i sgron //
NK039(ti)019:374: zhun chen mdangs kyi mar me 'di //
NK039(ti)019:375: ma yi spyan la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:376: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:377: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:378: a lo ke khrag chen dug dang sbyar ba yis //
NK039(ti)019:380: ma yi thugs kar thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:381: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:382: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:383: g+han+de phye ma lnga yi bshos bu dang //
NK039(ti)019:384: nal sha yon tan lnga ldan 'di //
NK039(ti)019:385: ma yi ljags la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:386: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:387: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:388: ne wi t+ya pi wam gling bu mkhar ba'i rnga //
NK039(ti)019:389: b+han+d+ha cha lang rkang gi dung //
NK039(ti)019:390: ma yi snyan la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:391: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)019:392: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:393: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti sa pa ri wa ra shab+da pra tits+tsha h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)019:394: de rnams phyi yi mchod pa'o //
NK039(ti)019:395: de nas nang mchod 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:396: badz+ra ma h+aa ka li re ma ti h'u /
NK039(ti)019:399: de nas gtor ma byin gyis rlabs te 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:401: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)019:402: bum dang ril dang phyed tshal dang //
NK039(ti)019:403: nang rol glo snying mkhal mar bcas //
NK039(ti)019:404: sha dang rus pa rkang tshil rnams //
NK039(ti)019:406: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:407: dgra bo ma h+aa mang sa la kha kha kh+aa h+ai kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:408: rak+ta la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:409: tsit+ta la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:410: ba su ta la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:411: ko ro tsa na la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:412: king ni ri ti la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:413: skye mched bcu gnyis la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:414: srog dang dbugs la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:417: ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)019:418: dam tshig dbang gi snying khrag dmar la rol //
NK039(ti)019:419: ma cig khrag 'thung dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)019:420: dam rdzas rmad du byung ba'i dmar chen khrag la rol //
NK039(ti)019:421: ma h+aa rak+ta la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:424: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:425: ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)019:426: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskangs ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:427: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes shig /
NK039(ti)019:428: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:431: ma cig chen mo 'khor bcas la //
NK039(ti)019:432: yang gcig mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:433: mi dbang 'bras bu'i sha phyed dang //
NK039(ti)019:434: 'chi ka'i mtshal tig dmar po dang //
NK039(ti)019:435: shing lo rlung khyer sa la ma reg dang //
NK039(ti)019:436: 'bras bu smin pa'i shing tog dang //
NK039(ti)019:437: na chung ma yi byung zad khrag /
NK039(ti)019:438: dam nyams byang sems dkar dmar dang //
NK039(ti)019:439: dri rgod snying dang dbang po lnga //
NK039(ti)019:440: bong bu'i snying dang khrims 'chal sha /
NK039(ti)019:441: rnam lnga bdud rtsis mchod pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)019:443: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:444: bsten pa'i dam rdzas la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:445: bsten pa'i dam rdzas kyis mchod pa 'bul /
NK039(ti)019:447: ma cig chen mo 'khor bcas rnams //
NK039(ti)019:448: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)019:449: ma yi bu la dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)019:450: ye shes gsang ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:451: 'dod khams 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:452: 'jig rten dbang du sdud pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:453: tshe dang longs spyod rgyas pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:454: ye shes lnga yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:455: grub chen brgyad kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:456: phrin las bzhi'i sku gsung thugs kyi sh+r+ai de bi
NK039(ti)019:457: ma h+aa ka li ka ya wak+ka tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha
NK039(ti)019:458: la h'u +aah zhes dngos grub blang ngo //
NK039(ti)019:460: bskal pa'i me rlung 'tshubs ma'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)019:461: ma cig lha mo nag mo glog 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)019:462: pho nya bdud kyi bu mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)019:463: ma cig 'khor bcas brtse bas dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:464: bdag nyid mi mkhas rmongs pa'i dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)019:465: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gis //
NK039(ti)019:466: ting 'dzin ma gsal rab rib khal khol dang //
NK039(ti)019:467: sngags dang phyag rgya'i gra chags zur nyams dang //
NK039(ti)019:468: nyams pa can gyi skyon gyis phog pa dang //
NK039(ti)019:469: phud nyams lhag mar gyur pa thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)019:470: dam rdzas mchod rdzas dus su ma 'tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)019:471: dpon dang mched lcam thugs dang 'gal ba dang //
NK039(ti)019:472: khyad par ma cig lha mo'i dam tshig las //
NK039(ti)019:473: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gis //
NK039(ti)019:474: nyams chag zhig ral gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)019:475: ma cig bdud mo 'bum tshogs rnams la bshags //
NK039(ti)019:476: rab tu bshags pas tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)019:478: de nas bskang rdzas rnams gzhung ltar byin gyis rlabs so //
NK039(ti)019:479: sngags drug dang phyag drug la sogs pa gzhung bzhin bya'o //
NK039(ti)019:480: de nas rol mo dbyangs dang bcas pa'i /
NK039(ti)019:481: rgyas pa spro na gzer chung bskang ba ring thung gnyis /
NK039(ti)019:482: bskang thung 'di dang gsum 'don par bya'o //
NK039(ti)019:483: mi spro na 'di las 'dus par snang ngo //
NK039(ti)019:485: dpal ldan lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:486: sring gcig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:487: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:488: nad dang rim gyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:489: thugs dam bskang phyir gnas 'dir byon //
NK039(ti)019:490: nyams chag gso phyir gnas 'dir byon //
NK039(ti)019:491: phrin las sgrub phyir gnas 'dir byon //
NK039(ti)019:492: bskang ngo skal par thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:493: 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //

NK039(ti)019:495: bsten pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:496: mi dbang snying gi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:497: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan 'dren phyir //
NK039(ti)019:498: mi rkang gling bu'i thugs dam bskang //

NK039(ti)019:500: bdud rtsi sman gyi thugs dam bskang //

NK039(ti)019:502: rma bya'i rgyal mtshan gyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:503: ljags kyi dbang po tshim bya'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:504: sha chen rus pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:505: mgrin pa'i gsang nas sbyangs ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:506: dmar chen rak+tasa thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:507: tshil chen dri la snoms pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:508: gsur chen dud pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:510: rgyun gyi gtor mas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:511: nyams chag ma lus bskang ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)019:512: bya nag g.yag nag lug nag gi //
NK039(ti)019:513: nag mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:515: dkar mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:516: dmar mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:517: ser mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:518: ljang mo 'bum sde'i sngon mo 'bum sde'i mthing nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:519: dmar nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:520: ser nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:521: ljang nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:522: sngo nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:523: smug nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:524: ma ye shes rgyal mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:525: bod skyong brtan ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:526: 'dzam gling skyong ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)019:527: ma khyod kyang dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)019:529: gal te dam la khyod 'da' na //
NK039(ti)019:530: srog gi snying po me 'bar bas //
NK039(ti)019:531: rang srog rang gi gcod par byed //
NK039(ti)019:532: de bas dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)019:533: thugs dam gnyen po 'dir skong la //
NK039(ti)019:534: nyams chag ci mchis bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)019:535: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)019:536: phrin las drag shul mthu ma chung //
NK039(ti)019:537: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK039(ti)019:538: gnod pa'i bgegs la phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:539: phas kyi rbod gtong bzlog tu gsol //
NK039(ti)019:540: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:541: de nas bstan pa bsrungs ba'i ched du 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:543: 'phrul gyi pho brang thod pa'i lding khang nas //
NK039(ti)019:544: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:545: srin po nag po'i chung ma ral pa can //
NK039(ti)019:546: ya mtshan rmad byung lha mo 'phros pa'i gtso //
NK039(ti)019:547: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs drag po'i rkan sgra rdebs //
NK039(ti)019:548: rngam pa'i tshul gyis dmar chen khrag la rol //
NK039(ti)019:549: kha 'bar chen mo srog gi shan pa mo //
NK039(ti)019:550: kha mchu chen mo srog gis tsa la mo //
NK039(ti)019:551: mkha' 'gro chen mo bse' gdong las mkhan ma //
NK039(ti)019:552: sku ni nag mo 'bum gyi dbus su bzhugs //
NK039(ti)019:553: skye ba rnam bzhi bsgrol ba'i ging chen mo //
NK039(ti)019:554: khyed ni srid pa kun gyi bkur bar 'os //
NK039(ti)019:555: tshangs pa'i rgyal po'i rma bya'i rgyal mtshan phul //
NK039(ti)019:556: nam mkha'i lha bran rnams kyi sil snyan dril bu phul //
NK039(ti)019:557: 'chi bdag rgyal pos phyag na ral gri phul //
NK039(ti)019:558: bdud kyi rgyal pos khram bam nag po phul //
NK039(ti)019:559: dur khrod bdag pos b+han+d+ha lcang lo phul //
NK039(ti)019:560: gnod sbyin rgyal pos ne'u le'i rkyal pa phul //
NK039(ti)019:561: rnam thos sras kyi seng ge'i snyan cha phul //
NK039(ti)019:562: khyab 'jug chen pos nyi ma zla ba phul //
NK039(ti)019:563: theg chen rgyal pos glang chen ko rlon phul //
NK039(ti)019:564: ma bdud rgyal mos re lde sham thabs phul //
NK039(ti)019:565: ma mo rnams kyis nad kyi rkyal pa phul //
NK039(ti)019:566: klu mo rnams kyi 'phrul gyi me long phul //
NK039(ti)019:567: sman mo rnams kyis tshon gyi gru gu phul //
NK039(ti)019:568: sha za'i rgyal pos thod pa'i phreng ba phul //
NK039(ti)019:569: lha srin rnams kyis gser gyi dril bu phul //
NK039(ti)019:570: sa bdag rgyal pos rus sbal pho gu phul //
NK039(ti)019:571: btsan gyi rgyal pos shwa d+hil dkar nag phul //
NK039(ti)019:572: srin po'i rgyal pos lcags sgrog 'bar ba phul //
NK039(ti)019:573: rgyal po dkar pos spyan mig g.yas pa phul //
NK039(ti)019:574: rnal 'byor bdag gi bdud rtsi gtor ma phul //
NK039(ti)019:575: rak+ta dmar gyi ar+g+ha bskyed pa nas //
NK039(ti)019:576: ma la bus bos gdung sems ma chung bar //
NK039(ti)019:577: smug nag 'jigs pa'i rgyal mo sku bzhengs la //
NK039(ti)019:578: lcags kyu 'dra ba'i sder mos gtor ma longs //
NK039(ti)019:579: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i zhal gdongs la //
NK039(ti)019:580: za byed rno gdug 'bar ba'i mche ba gtsigs //
NK039(ti)019:581: le brgan khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i ljags rkyong la //
NK039(ti)019:582: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam zhing mgul la bstim //
NK039(ti)019:583: kha kha kh+aa ram kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:585: dur khrod mnga' mdzad lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:586: 'das dang ma 'ongs da lta kun la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)019:587: stong gsum 'jig rten khams kyi gzugs 'phrog ma //
NK039(ti)019:588: blo med grogs 'tshol blon po rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:589: 'jigs pa'i mgon skyob dmag dpon rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:590: mi 'bral zung 'jug btsun mo rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:591: theg pa'i don dam glang po rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:592: sa bcu bgrod pa'i rta mchog rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:593: gzhan la dbang bsgyur 'khor lo rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:594: bsam 'phel don ldan nor bu rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:595: 'jig rten mgon po ltar ni bsod nams 'phel //
NK039(ti)019:596: lha dbang brgya byin ltar ni longs spyod che //
NK039(ti)019:597: u ma de ba ltar ni che lugs btsun //
NK039(ti)019:598: u dum war ba ltar ni skye bar dkon //
NK039(ti)019:599: me tog pad+ma ltar ni lha rdzas mdzes //
NK039(ti)019:600: nam mkha'i lha bran ltar ni sku 'khrungs legs //
NK039(ti)019:601: gcan gzan seng ge ltar ni gzhan la brjid //
NK039(ti)019:602: phyag na rdo rje ltar na mthu stobs che //
NK039(ti)019:603: 'jam dpal gzhon nu ltar ni shes rab che //
NK039(ti)019:604: spyan ras gzigs dbang ltar ni thugs rje che //
NK039(ti)019:605: spyi gtsug nor bu ltar ni gtsug na 'bar //
NK039(ti)019:606: 'dzam gling rgyal po ltar ni rtag tu bstod //
NK039(ti)019:607: dpal ldan re ma ti la bdag gis bstod //
NK039(ti)019:608: de nas brten gtor me rlung gang rung gis sbyor bas byin gyis rlabs la 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:609: sngags kyi gsham du b+ha ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:610: zhes pa thod pa'i phyag rgya bcing la lan gnyis sam gsum mam bdun gyis 'bul la /
NK039(ti)019:611: lha mo 'khor dang bcas pas gsol nas mnyes par bsam la /
NK039(ti)019:612: de ni gnas gzhi'i dmigs pa byas la /
NK039(ti)019:614: bdag gi thugs ka'i sngags phreng h'uhdang bcas pa las
NK039(ti)019:615: 'od zer dkar po gcig sku yi dbyibs mar brgyud
NK039(ti)019:616: nas / rdo rje nor bu'i rtser byung nas byang
NK039(ti)019:617: chub sems kyi mchod pa rnams phul bas mnyes shing
NK039(ti)019:618: nas / tshim par bsam / 'od zer yang lha
NK039(ti)019:619: mo'i sku'i dbyibs mar brgyud nas b+h+yo la g.yon du
NK039(ti)019:620: nas / tshim par bsam / bskor bas / bdag
NK039(ti)019:621: la 'gal ba dang nyes skyon thams cad dag par
NK039(ti)019:622: nas / tshim par bsam / bskor bas / bsam
NK039(ti)019:623: / lha mo'i zhal nas bdag gi zhal du tshur
NK039(ti)019:624: zhugs pa'i dus su yi ge gsum gyi sna drangs
NK039(ti)019:625: nas mchog thun mong gi dngos grub dang phrin las
NK039(ti)019:626: rnam pa bzhi'i dngos grub dang mthu stobs nus pa
NK039(ti)019:627: byin rlabs thams cad bdag la phul bas /
NK039(ti)019:628: bdag bkrag gzi mdangs nus pa mthu stobs thams cad dang ldan pa'i /
NK039(ti)019:629: khams gsum thams cad dus gcig tu sgrol nus pa gcig bsgom /
NK039(ti)019:630: nad dang gnod pa rkyen dang bar chad thams cad zhi bar bsam /
NK039(ti)019:631: de nas bdag gi thugs ka'i sngags phreng h'u dang
NK039(ti)019:632: bcas pa las 'od zer g.yas su lan gsum bskor
NK039(ti)019:633: ba'i lha mo 'khor bcas thams cad bdag gi dbang
NK039(ti)019:634: du 'dus nas bka' nyan gsungs sdod byed cing ci
NK039(ti)019:635: bcol pa'i las thams cad skad cig gis bsgrub par
NK039(ti)019:636: bsam / sngags ma yengs bar ting 'dzin dang ldan
NK039(ti)019:637: pa'i rtags ma byung gi bar du zhag gcig gi
NK039(ti)019:638: bar thun bzhir byas la bzlas pa /
NK039(ti)019:640: yang na bdag gi ci rigs bar du bsnyen pa bazla'o //
NK039(ti)019:641: ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti h'u /
NK039(ti)019:643: b+h+yo ma mo nag mo be ta li sid+d+hi ku
NK039(ti)019:644: lu ku lu ma h+aa b+aa lim ta kha kha
NK039(ti)019:648: ru ru ro ru p+ai tish+tha ba to p+ai tsa
NK039(ti)019:649: wa la a shug me b+h+yohmh'u dzah 'jug la ma
NK039(ti)019:650: h+aa ka li sogs tshar gcig /
NK039(ti)019:652: snying po nye snying srog sngags 'di gsum re re
NK039(ti)019:653: la 'bum phrag re bzlas dngos grub kyi mtshan ma'o
NK039(ti)019:654: // grangs bsnyen 'bum phrag gsum bye ba gcig bzlas na phyag mtshan mthong /
NK039(ti)019:655: sa ya gcig bzlas na lha mo mngon du mthong /
NK039(ti)019:656: de nas bsnyen sngags la nan tan byed pa gal che'o //
NK039(ti)019:657: yi ge brgya pa kha skong ngo //
NK039(ti)019:658: de nas nang gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:659: dpal ldan lha mo 'khor dang bcas pa'i ljags h'u
NK039(ti)019:660: las skyes pa'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa dmar po
NK039(ti)019:661: 'od kyi sbu gu can du gyur nas gtor ma'i
NK039(ti)019:662: bcud drangs nas gsol bar gyur /
NK039(ti)019:663: ma ma de bi ka li re ma ti ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)019:664: a mri ta p+au dza ho /
NK039(ti)019:665: zhes pa lan gsum gyi gtso mo dang 'bod rbad
NK039(ti)019:666: bsad gsum gyi sngags ring gi lan gsum gtso 'khor
NK039(ti)019:668: ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti sa pa ri wa ra ar+g+ham ces pa nas /
NK039(ti)019:669: shab+da pra tits+tsha h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)019:670: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti h'u /
NK039(ti)019:673: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las mgon //
NK039(ti)019:674: rang bzhin don rdzogs phyir mi ldog pa'i yum //
NK039(ti)019:675: gzhon nu'i tshul 'chang sa brgyad gnon pa mo //
NK039(ti)019:676: ral gri ne'u le 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)019:678: de nas bstod pa bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:680: dpal gyi srung ma khams gsum gtso mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:681: bong bu'i rta mchog dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)019:682: re lde'i stod g.yog sbrul gyi sham thabs can //
NK039(ti)019:683: 'bar ba'i dbang rtags phyag na ral gri bsnams //
NK039(ti)019:684: lte bar nyi shar gtsug na zla rgyas gsal //
NK039(ti)019:685: nag mo khrag 'thung dbyings kyi dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)019:686: khram bam nad kyi rkyal pa phyag na bsnams //
NK039(ti)019:687: nag mo re ma ti la bdag gis bstod //
NK039(ti)019:688: bdag gi btsun par khyod bstod nas //
NK039(ti)019:689: khyod la bcol ba'i las rnams ni //
NK039(ti)019:690: yud tsam gcig gis 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:692: yang thog dgu brtsegs 'phrul gyi pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)019:693: ma cig lha mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:694: sku mdog nyi 'od 'bar ba'i sman gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:695: sku ni mi 'gyur ri rab lhun po 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:696: gsungs snyan 'brug sgra nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam //
NK039(ti)019:697: thugs kyi dpal be'u ye shes lnga dang ldan //
NK039(ti)019:698: mgul gyi bum pa rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra //
NK039(ti)019:699: phan gnod myur du bsgrub pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)019:700: ljags ni pad+ma le brgan dung swo bzhed //
NK039(ti)019:701: bstan pa srung mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)019:702: bstan pa rgyas mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)019:703: dgra bgegs 'dul mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)019:704: bu nor mthu'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)019:705: de nas dpal ldan lha mo la nam mkha'i lha
NK039(ti)019:706: bran rnams kyis rtag gis sgo nas bstod pa ni
NK039(ti)019:708: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)019:709: rlung nag dgu rlung 'khyil pa'i pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)019:710: ma cig lha mo nag mo 'dod khams gtso //
NK039(ti)019:711: nag mo za byed 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK039(ti)019:712: mthing nag mi srin khrag gi ral pa can //
NK039(ti)019:713: ma khyod kyi sku mdog nag mor ston pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:714: don dam dbyings nas skye ba med pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:715: ral pa g.yas dang g.yon du 'khyil //
NK039(ti)019:716: yum gyi mkha' la sprul pa 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:717: ral pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:718: thugs rje'i sprul sku phyogs bcur 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:719: ral pa spyi bor gtsug tu 'khyil pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:720: thugs dam dgongs spyod gcig tu mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:721: rma bya'i rgyal mtshan dbu la gtsug pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:722: phrin las rnam bzhi so sor mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:723: thod skam phreng bas dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:724: thugs rje'i sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:725: snyan cha g.yas na seng ge 'phyo ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:726: dman mo thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:727: snyan cha g.yon nas sbrul nag 'phyo ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:728: zhe sdang ma spangs dbyings su dag pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:729: snyan cha gser gyi dril bu dkrol ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:730: sangs rgyas rnams la bsnyen bskur byed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:731: spyan gsum dmar zlum phyogs bcur bgrad pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:732: srid gsum rnal 'byor bya ra mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:733: zhal ni drag po'i hom khung gdangs pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:734: dgra bgegs gang yin zhal du gsol ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:735: rno gdugs mche ba zur gsum gtsig pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:736: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'i sha la rol pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:737: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:738: chos nyid yang dag don dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:739: glang chen ko rlon gos su gon pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:740: theg pa mchog gi don dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:741: nam phyed re lde nag pos dkris pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:742: 'jig rten 'di na che btsan ldan pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:743: stag gi lpags pas sham thabs byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:744: drag po'i cha lugs mngon du mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:745: lte ba'i dbus nas nyi ma shar ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:746: srid pa'i rgya mtsho gting nas skem pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:747: spyi bo'i gtsug nas zla ba rgyas pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:748: ma rig mun pa gting nas sel ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:749: phyag g.yas bdud kyi ral gri bsnams pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:750: dgra bgegs skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:751: phyag g.yon b+han+d+ha dmar chen bsnams pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:752: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal khrag ltar 'thung ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:753: mchan nas ne'u le'i rkyal pa bsnams pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:754: sgrub pa po la dngos grub ster ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:755: zhabs la dbang gi lcags sgrog bsgrogs pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:756: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:757: phyir phyogs bong bu dmar ka bcibs pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:758: log par lta ba'i dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:759: srin po'i ya mgal snga ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:760: srin yul lang+ka pu ri bsgrod pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:761: srin mo'i ma mgal phyi ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:762: bdud dang gshin rje'i gdug pa dul ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:763: gong thag glo smed sbrul las byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:764: zhe sdang gdug pa chen po 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:765: rus sbal nag po pho ku btab pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:766: klu bdud ma rung dam la 'dog pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:767: snga shad bdud kyi khram bam btags pa ni //
NK039(ti)019:768: dam nyams dgra bo khram la 'debs pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:769: phyi shad nad kyi rkyal pa bkal ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:770: bstan pa'i dgra la na kha 'bebs pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:771: don dam bcud kyi rtags su zhag gis zo ris byas //
NK039(ti)019:772: thugs rje'i chags pas rtags su rak+ta'i thig le'i brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:773: 'dul byed phrin las rtags su thal chen tshom bus byug /
NK039(ti)019:774: ma mo 'bum phrag bran du 'khol ba ni //
NK039(ti)019:775: stong khams khyab par dbang du bsdus pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)019:776: ma cig kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skem //
NK039(ti)019:777: lag na rdo 'phen ri rab si bur bsil //
NK039(ti)019:778: lha mo khyed la bdag gi btsun par bstod //
NK039(ti)019:779: dpal ldan lha mo mthu chen ma //
NK039(ti)019:780: chos skyong rgyal mo mi bzad ma //
NK039(ti)019:781: gsang ba'i dbang phyug rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)019:782: bstan pa bsrung mdzad dam la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)019:783: rgyud 'bum nas 'byung ba ltar lha mo dpal bzhi'i bstod do //
NK039(ti)019:785: dpal ldan lha mo khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)019:786: dpal chen dpal dang ldan pa'i bdag nyid ma //
NK039(ti)019:787: 'gro ba thugs rjes skyobs mdzad byams chen ma //
NK039(ti)019:788: mi mthun phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba mo //
NK039(ti)019:789: dngos grub bdag la stsol cig dpal ldan ma //
NK039(ti)019:790: mdzes shing yid 'ongs mtshan dpa'i rab brgyan ma //
NK039(ti)019:791: srid gsum kun du gzi brjid dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)019:792: 'jig rten grags pa zil gyis gnon pa mo //
NK039(ti)019:793: dngos grub myur du stsol cig bdag nyid ma //
NK039(ti)019:794: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer rab 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)019:795: dngos grub bzang por stsol cig mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)019:796: bde chen bde ba'i ye shes kun rdzogs ma //
NK039(ti)019:797: dpal chen sku la dgyes par 'khril sbyor ma //
NK039(ti)019:798: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dpal dang dgra bla mo //
NK039(ti)019:799: mchog gis dngos grub stsol cig yum mchog ma //
NK039(ti)019:800: nag mo bzang mo 'jigs pa'i gzugs can ma //
NK039(ti)019:801: shes rab ral gris ma rig rtsad gcod ma //
NK039(ti)019:802: ne'u le'i dgos 'dod re ba skong ba mo //
NK039(ti)019:803: nad dang gdon rnams sol cig dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)019:804: yon tan kun rdzogs dbyings phyug nam gru ma //
NK039(ti)019:805: lang ka pu ri'i grong khyer 'jigs mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)019:806: srin po'i bong bu zhabs kyis gnon pa mo //
NK039(ti)019:807: thugs rjes rtag tu gzigs shig ma cig ma //
NK039(ti)019:808: theg chen don ldan glang chen gos 'dzin ma //
NK039(ti)019:809: stong gsum 'tshubs ma'i nang nas 'gro mgyogs ma //
NK039(ti)019:810: gsang sngags bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor skyong ba mo //
NK039(ti)019:811: bdag la byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)019:812: yid 'ong dung mdog dkar la rgyan mdzes ma //
NK039(ti)019:813: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams sel mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)019:814: nad bdag 'chi gdon nad rnams sel ba mo //
NK039(ti)019:815: nad rnams zhi bar mdzod cig ral gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:816: rin chen rgyan dang gser mdog brjid 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)019:817: rgyal srid nor kyang dang ldan 'byor ldan ma //
NK039(ti)019:818: yid bzhin nor ltar dgos 'dod skong ba mo //
NK039(ti)019:819: bstan pa rgyas par spel cig dpa' 'phel ma //
NK039(ti)019:820: phrin las kun la mnga' mdzad las mkhan ma //
NK039(ti)019:821: thod le brtsegs pa'i mkhar nas rab brjid ma //
NK039(ti)019:822: gnas mchog byang shar mtshams na bzhugs pa mo //
NK039(ti)019:823: dgra bgegs dbang du bsdus shig yum mchog ma //
NK039(ti)019:824: lha chen chung ma rde sogs kun sbyar ma //
NK039(ti)019:825: lha min g.yul bzlog dka' thub ral gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:826: dbang phyug sras mo dkar mo dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)019:827: gshin rje'i lcam gcig rak+ta tsa mun di //
NK039(ti)019:828: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs thul cig re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:829: bdag la gnod pa'i gdon dang bgegs la sogs //
NK039(ti)019:830: mi mthun phyogs rnams zhi ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)019:831: 'gro rnams rtag tu byams dang snying rje yis //
NK039(ti)019:832: dbang du bsdus nas bdag dang gcig tu mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:833: dkon mchog sku dgra bstan pa'i ru tra dang //
NK039(ti)019:834: rdo rje slob dpon sku dgrar gyur pa dang //
NK039(ti)019:835: rnal 'byor bdag la gnod pa yi //
NK039(ti)019:836: dgra bgegs rnam shes 'gugs dang gsod dang bskrad pa dang //
NK039(ti)019:837: thams cad rdul phran bzhin du brlag pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:838: sngon tshe rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas che mchog he ru ka /
NK039(ti)019:839: phyag na rdo rje pad+ma 'byung gnas dang //
NK039(ti)019:840: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i bka' la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)019:841: bdag gi bcol pa'i las rnams 'grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK039(ti)019:842: skabs 'dir bsgral las rgyas par bya'o //
NK039(ti)019:843: de nas bskul pa bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)019:844: b+h+yoh kye ma nad dang rim gyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:845: gshin rje'i khams kyi sring gcig ma //
NK039(ti)019:846: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)019:847: mdzes pa'i lan bu gcig ma la //
NK039(ti)019:848: re lde mdzes pas rnam par brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:849: rkang la lcags kyi lhwam gyon ma //
NK039(ti)019:850: phyir phyogs dril gyi pha la bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:851: 'byung po phal cher kun gyi bdag /
NK039(ti)019:852: 'byung po yongs kyi sha la chem chem gsol //
NK039(ti)019:853: mi khrag chang gi ra ros myos //
NK039(ti)019:854: dpag tshad brgyad khrir bzhi stong yang //
NK039(ti)019:855: mtshan mo gcig la khyab par nyul //
NK039(ti)019:856: rnal 'byor chen mo a la la //
NK039(ti)019:857: dbang phyug chen mo a la la //
NK039(ti)019:858: gshin rje'i lcam gcig a la la //
NK039(ti)019:859: bdud kyi yum gcig a la la //
NK039(ti)019:860: mdog bzang nag mo a la la //
NK039(ti)019:861: e ma nad dang rim gyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:862: re 'gas drag tu khros pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)019:863: sku ni nag mo chen mo la //
NK039(ti)019:864: bud med nag mos stong khams khengs //
NK039(ti)019:865: ral pa'i se lan mun ltar gtib //
NK039(ti)019:866: spyan nas khrag gi mchi ma 'dzag /
NK039(ti)019:867: shang nas nad kyi rlangs pa 'thul //
NK039(ti)019:869: g.yas nas mi lpags g.yang gzhi rdebs //
NK039(ti)019:870: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal ba bsnams //
NK039(ti)019:871: nad dang rim gyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:872: 'dir gshegs brgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)019:873: bdag gis bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:874: de nas dmag bskul byed yin /
NK039(ti)019:876: ma ri smug nag dgu klung nas //
NK039(ti)019:877: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)019:878: bdud mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:879: rdo rje khros mo gtum bag can //
NK039(ti)019:880: bal nad rgyu gzer bdag mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:881: skye shi gnyis kyi mnga' bdag mo //
NK039(ti)019:882: thod pa dgu brtsegs mkhar na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)019:883: ral pa khrag gi char pa 'bebs //
NK039(ti)019:884: spyan dmar rdo rje'i glog stong 'gyu //
NK039(ti)019:885: rkan sgra rdabs pas bdud dpung 'joms //
NK039(ti)019:886: mkha' la bzhad pas gnam lcags ser chen 'bebs //
NK039(ti)019:887: phyag na gsod pa'i khram bam thogs //
NK039(ti)019:888: nad kyi rkyal pa dgra la b+h+yo bzlog mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:889: thod dmar rdo rje phreng bas brgyan //
NK039(ti)019:890: bdud kyi dril nag rkang gsum bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:891: bdud kyi mnga' bdag rjes gcod ma //
NK039(ti)019:892: dgra bo gsod pa'i dus la bab /
NK039(ti)019:894: sprul pa phyag brnyan klu mo chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)019:895: sbrul nag chen po'i gdu bu can //
NK039(ti)019:896: su dang 'phrad na srog la rgol //
NK039(ti)019:897: dgra bo gsod pa'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)019:898: rdo rje ba lam drel sna ma //
NK039(ti)019:899: khrag gi ral pa'i cod pan can //
NK039(ti)019:900: sku la re lde gos su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:901: phyag na zhing gi g.yang gzhi rdebs //
NK039(ti)019:902: chibs su dril nag rkang gsum bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:903: dus la bab po sa ma ya //
NK039(ti)019:904: rdo rje khri sman sa le ma //
NK039(ti)019:905: gser g.yu spel ma'i chu 'khor can //
NK039(ti)019:906: sku la le brgan gos su gsol //
NK039(ti)019:907: phyag na chu srin rgyal mtshan thogs //
NK039(ti)019:908: chibs su sol bya rog mo bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:909: 'dir spyon bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:910: de nas drag bskul byed pa ni /
NK039(ti)019:912: ma g.yel ma g.yel dam la dgongs //
NK039(ti)019:913: ma g.yel ma g.yel ma cig ma //
NK039(ti)019:914: ma g.yel ma g.yel bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)019:915: ma cig lha mo dpal ldan ma //
NK039(ti)019:916: rdo rje lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:917: nad dang rim gyi mnga' bdag mo //
NK039(ti)019:918: sad dang ser ba'i sna 'dren ma //
NK039(ti)019:919: dam nyams kun gyi srog gcod ma //
NK039(ti)019:920: dam tshig can gyi grogs mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)019:921: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dgra bla mo //
NK039(ti)019:922: skye 'gro'i srog la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)019:923: 'byung po yongs kyi rje mo khyod //
NK039(ti)019:924: dgra bo dus mtha' sdud byed ma //
NK039(ti)019:925: srid gsum za ba'i las mkhan mo //
NK039(ti)019:926: khams gsum za ba'i mthu mo che //
NK039(ti)019:927: mthing nag gcer bu khrag gi ral pa can //
NK039(ti)019:928: mig nas khrag gi mchi ma 'dzag /
NK039(ti)019:929: shang nas nad kyi dud pa 'thul //
NK039(ti)019:930: chibs su dril sngon rlung gshog bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:931: re 'ga' khros na ca co byed //
NK039(ti)019:932: srin po'i bong bu dmar gwa bcibs //
NK039(ti)019:933: g.yas nas gdug pa'i ral gri phyar //
NK039(ti)019:934: g.yon nas gdug pa'i thod khrag thogs //
NK039(ti)019:935: skye 'gro'i srog la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)019:936: ma g.yel ma g.yel dam la dgongs //
NK039(ti)019:937: ma cig bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:938: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum sde rnams //
NK039(ti)019:939: bu la sdang ba'i dgra byung gis //
NK039(ti)019:940: ma cig lha mo rab mda' log /
NK039(ti)019:941: sdang ba'i dgra la phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)019:942: ma cig thugs dam dus la bab //
NK039(ti)019:943: bcol pa'i las la mthu ma chung //
NK039(ti)019:944: dam tshig gnyen la ma 'da' bar //

NK039(ti)019:947: ma cig bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)019:948: khyod kyi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)019:949: las kyi pho nya bdud mo 'bum //

NK039(ti)019:951: ma bdud nag mo 'khor dang bcas //

NK039(ti)019:954: kha nas gdug pa'i ngan sngags bzlog /
NK039(ti)019:956: nad kyi kha phus dgra la thobs //

NK039(ti)019:958: ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)019:959: bdag gi las su khyed mchod na //
NK039(ti)019:960: bdag la sdang ba'i dgra bo 'di //
NK039(ti)019:961: lo dang zla ba ma bzhag par //
NK039(ti)019:962: zhag dang za ma'i dus mtha' sdus //

NK039(ti)019:978: zas su mi sha rta sha za //
